This is the changelog of VulkanExtended

b1.00:
   -First release, with Vulkan 1.2.197 (dynamic rendering) support

b1.03:
   -Partial Vulkan 1.3 support

b1.07
   -Removed DEF file
   -Increased Vulkan 1.3 support
   -Removed vulkan-1-real.dll need, so now, no real dll to paste next to the wrapper
   -Added a bunch of others things that didn't work...

b1.11
   -Replaced some stubs by working functions
   -Added a test support for Vulkan 1.2.170 GPU (GCN/Windows 7). Games may not work but full support is in progress
